28. Qd5! (28. Rxe5+ { In the game the tempting 28.Rxe5 was played and after } 28... Kxf4 29. Re2 Qd3 { Black king is totally safe and white was losing } 30. Rhe1 { 1/2-1/2 The game is a draw. }) 28... Kxf4 (28... Rge8 29. Bxe5 Rxe5 30. Rhf1+ Kg6 31. Qf7+ Kg5 32. Qf6+ Kg4 33. Rf4+ Kh5 34. Rh4#) 29. Rhf1+ Kg5 (29... Kg4 30. Qe6+ Kg5 31. Qf6+ Kg4 32. Rf4+) 30. Rxe5+! { Now this is the winning move and the only one! } 30... Bxe5 31. Qxe5+ Kh6 (31... Kg6 32. Qxg3+ Kh7 33. Rh1#) 32. Qf6+ { and White mates in 2 moves. } { [%cal Gf1h1] } 1/2-1/2


