92. Ng4! { The only move to win. } (92. Nc4 Bg5 93. Ne3 Bf6?? { is the topic of next chapter. } 94. Nd5+ { 1-0 White wins. }) 92... Bg5 93. Nh6! { The idea is to get Ne7 unhindered. } 93... Bh4 (93... Kd6 94. Nf7+ { is Black can put his king to e6 then it's a draw. } (94. Nf5+ Ke6)) 94. Nf5 Bg5 95. Ne7 1-0


