{ Let's start with the Turkish Star's game against the World Champion! }
27... Ba6 28. Rad1! (28. Rxa6 { This is the game continuation. } 28... bxa6 29. Qxa6 Qd4 $17 { Black won in the end. }) 28... Qe7 29. Qxe8+!! { A brilliant resource underlining black's back rank problems! } 29... Qxe8 30. Rxe4! Qf8 31. Red4! { The only way to win. } 31... Bb5 32. Rd8 Be8 33. Re1! $18 { Important last detail, White is winning. } 0-1


