50. Ne3 { This time Oro is on the defensive side. White is pawn down but fighting on, but his last move gives Black an opportunity. } 50... Rxe3! 51. fxe3 Qxe3+ { [%cal Gg1h2,Ye3e5,Be5h2,Ge5a1] } 52. Kh1 Be4! 53. Qb6 Qxh3+ 54. Kg1 Qe3+ 55. Kh1 { Warmardam decides to repeat once here. } 55... Qh3+ 56. Kg1 Qe3+ 57. Kh1 Qd4! { [%csl Ga1] } 58. Re1 Nb4! { All of Black's forces coordinating well and White has no defence against the threats. } { [%csl Ge1,Rf1][%cal Gb4c2] } 59. Qc7 Nc2 60. Rc1 (60. Rb1 Ne3 { [%csl Gb1] } 61. Rc1 (61. Re1 Bxg2+ $19 { [%cal Gd4h4,Gh4e1] }) 61... Qb2 $19 { [%cal Gb2g2,Gb2c1] }) 60... Qb2 61. Kg1 (61. Rd1 Ne3 $19) 61... Qxc1 62. Qe5+ Kg8 { Black repeats once more. } 63. Qe8+ Kg7 64. Qe5+ Kf8! 65. Qxc5+ Kg8 { White resigned as there's only one more check, and it's over. } 0-1


