65. g5+ Ke6 66. Kg4! { Now Black is in zugzwang! Black king should allow White king to enter no matter what he plays. } (66. gxh6 { This was the game continuation } 66... gxh6 67. Kg4 Kf6 68. Kf4 Ke6 69. Kg4 Kf6 70. Kf4 Ke6 { 1/2-1/2 The game is a draw. }) 66... hxg5 (66... Kd6 67. Kf5 Ke7 68. gxh6 gxh6 69. Kg6 Ke6 70. Kxh6 Kf6 71. Kh7 { If there were no d-pawns this would be a draw, but now White will collect the d-pawn and Black can not ge the opposition. }) 67. Kxg5 Kf7 { [%csl Gg6] } 68. Kf5 { and White wins. } 1/2-1/2


